title: Trump Not Planning To Appeal Travel Ban Ruling To Supreme Court - Fox Nation
text:
Trump Not Planning To Appeal Travel Ban Ruling To Supreme Court Published February 10, 2017 
Kellyanne Conway joins 'The O'Reilly Factor' to discuss the ruling on the travel ban and its potential impact on security 
By Jordan Fabian and Ben Kamisar, The Hill 
The Trump administration is not planning to appeal a temporary hold on the president's travel ban to the Supreme Court, a White House official said Friday. 
But the White House said it will forge ahead on the broader battle against a lawsuit challenging the executive order. 
The administration plans to continue defending the substance of the order in a Seattle-based federal district court, the official said.
